xm1014 blue steel.flavorText: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

xm1014 blue tire.description: It has been spray-painted with a black and blue tire tread pattern.

xm1014 bone machine.description: It has been chromed then overlayed with a semi transparent hydrographic pattern of nuclear skulls and bones.

xm1014 calicamo.description: It has been painted using a VariCamo patterned hydrographic.
xm1014 calicamo.flavorText: Rebuilding only comes in the wake of destruction

xm1014 charter.description: A tan-colored pattern of crests, scrawls, and text from the Magna Carta has been applied.
xm1014 charter.flavorText: Everyone is subject to due processâ€”even you

xm1014 elegant vines.description: A red and green flower pattern has been applied.
xm1014 elegant vines.flavorText: Some see a nuisance; I see beauty

xm1014 entombed.description: Entombed for millennia, this recently unearthed XM-1014 has been custom painted with blue wraps and Egyptian accents.

xm1014 fallout warning.description: It has been spray-painted with radiological warning hazard patterns.

xm1014 frost borre.description: A Norse inspired pattern of silver interlocking rings has been applied.

xm1014 grassland.description: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a grassland color scheme.

xm1014 heaven guard.description: It has been painted using a combination of subtly patterned hydrographics and dry-transfer decals of wings.
xm1014 heaven guard.flavorText: Sometimes the wings of an angel don't mean salvation

xm1014 hieroglyph.description: It has been custom painted with Egyptian hieroglyphs and ornaments.

xm1014 incinegator.description: A custom paint job resembling a gator spitting fire has been applied.

xm1014 jungle.description: This memento from Ruins has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a jungle color scheme.
xm1014 jungle.flavorText: For those with an appetite for destruction

xm1014 oxide blaze.description: A custom paint job has been applied with a rust-colored base and white detailing.
xm1014 oxide blaze.flavorText: Not to be used as a load-bearing support

xm1014 quicksilver.description: It has been painted using a translucent hydrographic with a terrain map motif over metallic silver paint.
xm1014 quicksilver.flavorText: Sometimes you need an unstable element to solve your problems - Kotaro Izaki, Breach Expert

xm1014 red leather.description: Its stock and grip have been wrapped in red leather.
xm1014 red leather.flavorText: Pack your baags. Let's go kill that sonofabitch... - The Oni and The Valkyrie Part 2

xm1014 red python.description: It has been painted with a snakeskin patterned hydrographic.
xm1014 red python.flavorText: I know you don't believe in the cause...and when I expose you, Valeria will have your head - The Shield and The Serpent Part 1

xm1014 scumbria.description: It has been subtly painted with metallic paints.
xm1014 scumbria.flavorText: Let's not be hasty: there may be another way to get Valeria's attention... - A Father's Love Part 3

xm1014 seasons.description: It has been hand painted with a randomized multicolored leaf pattern.
xm1014 seasons.flavorText: Spring, summer, fall, and rarely winter

xm1014 slipstream.description: It has been custom painted with smoky greys and vibrant blues.
xm1014 slipstream.flavorText: Patience, Elliott; they still have a role to play... - The Mercenary and The Serpent Part 2

xm1014 teclu burner.description: Metallic paint has been used to add flames.

xm1014 tranquility.description: It has been hand painted with the image of a woman with long hair.
xm1014 tranquility.flavorText: I'm not here for what I need; I'm here for something I want - Imogen and The Oni Part 2

xm1014 urban perforated.description: It has been spray-painted using ripped tape strips and perforated metal as stencils.

xm1014 varicamo blue.description: It has been painted using a VariCamo patterned hydrographic.
xm1014 varicamo blue.flavorText: Rebuilding only comes in the wake of destruction

xm1014 watchdog.description: It has been custom painted with a jade green base and two guardian lions watching either direction. A third lion has been painted beneath the rear sight.

xm1014 xoxo.description: A vividly colored, punk-inspired pattern has been applied.

xm1014 ziggy.description: It has been finished with a randomized pattern of chartreuse, purple, and silver.

xm1014 zombie offensive.description: A custom pattern of zombified Counter-Strike agents has been applied.
